HEADWORD: Microzyme
<hw>Mi"cro*zyme</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Micro-</ets>
+ Gr. <grk>zy`mh</grk> leaven.]</ety> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>A
